To start the Mongodb Container - sudo docker container start mongodb
To stop the Mongodb Container - sudo docker container stop mongodb
sudo docker container run -p 8000:8000 mongo_webserver
To run the Webserver Docker Container - 

CURL Commands

curl "http://localhost:8000/list"
curl "http://localhost:8000/create?item=socks&price=10"
curl "http://localhost:8000/price?item=socks"
curl "http://localhost:8000/update?item=socks&price=25"
curl "http://localhost:8000/delete?item=socks"